But I saw authentic, so I don't touch it. Yeah, you got issues. Yeah, people have problems. But who doesn't?

03:02:41.120 --> 03:02:44.760
So regardless, he changed my life with some of the things I heard.

03:02:44.761 --> 03:02:51.599
And like I said, his daughter—the prayer that I learned there changed me forever.

03:02:51.600 --> 03:03:06.959
And that's what you all come to: the glory of the anointing of the Holy Ghost.

03:03:06.960 --> 03:03:16.035
Brandon, thank you for sharing your prayer treasures; this is my new obsession. You're welcome.

03:03:16.037 --> 03:03:23.783
Like I said, I would never—what the Lord says regarding wealth transfer, especially crypto, I don't touch that.

03:03:23.784 --> 03:03:31.820
I tried; the Lord told me not to talk about crypto much. He said, 'That's not what I called you to do.

03:03:31.821 --> 03:03:43.501
I want you to pray, and when I warn you to warn them about crypto, you can, but it's not your vein.'And so I don't touch it until he tells me to.

03:03:43.502 --> 03:03:49.565
Can you say a prayer for—yeah, I pray for finances. 'Where does the word amen come from?

03:03:49.566 --> 03:03:56.579
Is there a true meaning?'Yes, I would love to come to your church. Please pray for Nigeria.

03:03:56.580 --> 03:04:05.119
Please answer how I break the poverty cycle of my life, also a generational curse biblically.

03:04:05.120 --> 03:04:20.288
Please call all chains of mine to be broken over your life. How you break poverty is with seedtime and harvest. You sow that. If you have a need, sow a seed. I give.

03:04:20.289 --> 03:04:34.478
'Give and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, running over shall men give into your bosom.'People don't realize you're never going to get out of poverty if you don't sow.

03:04:34.479 --> 03:04:39.835
Giving is your way out of poverty. And people don't want to hear that; they get ticked off.

03:04:39.836 --> 03:04:44.230
I'm telling you because prosperity got abused—always talking about things and people busting on it.

03:04:44.231 --> 03:04:50.059
And I'm telling you, it changed my life sowing and learning how to give.

03:04:50.060 --> 03:04:57.519
You cannot outgive God. He'll give you ideas to get wealth. He'll bless your hands to prosper.

03:04:57.520 --> 03:05:09.994
And people, they go, 'Well, I've always been poor,'because I don't talk down against prosperity, I don't talk down against healing, I keep believing it.

03:05:09.995 --> 03:05:16.558
And I go, 'Well, Lord, you're going to change my life.'Even if it's just a couple hundred bucks extra, that's a blessing.

03:05:16.559 --> 03:05:21.640
So I go, 'Hey,'but eBay and these other things that I've done have changed our life.

03:05:21.641 --> 03:05:30.899
It's not always been easy, but he's always provided for me. So what is prosperity to one is prosperity to the other—I don't know.

03:05:30.900 --> 03:05:39.252
To me, having more than enough to eat and take care of my kids, they have clothes in their bag and be able to get a camera for my thing is prosperity to me.

03:05:39.253 --> 03:05:43.965
Where you say, 'Hey, I'm not in lack.'When you live on food stamps, that's poor.

03:05:43.966 --> 03:05:48.113
And you go, 'Man, I don't have no food this week.'That's poverty to me.

03:05:48.114 --> 03:05:55.830
Now, for somebody's poverty, they could say, 'Brandon, you're in poverty where I'm at now.'And you go, 'You're in poverty,'but I'm happy.

03:05:55.831 --> 03:06:03.389
I'm blessed. Prosperity is all relevant. What is prosperity to you is probably not prosperity to me.

03:06:03.390 --> 03:06:09.519
My wife is healthy. I'm blessed. My marriage is good. That's prosperity.

03:06:09.520 --> 03:06:17.119
It doesn't have to be that I'm driving a Ferrari to say I'm rich or you've got a brand new whatever.

03:06:17.120 --> 03:06:21.753
Prosperity to me is my kids know Jesus; they're going to heaven.

03:06:21.754 --> 03:06:28.029
They can lay hands on any one of you all and I guarantee you God's going to heal them, probably more than likely if you have faith to believe.

03:06:28.030 --> 03:06:37.957
But I'm just saying that's prosperity to me. Now I might not have a jet like some of these ministers do; they think that's prosperous.

03:06:37.958 --> 03:06:49.839
But is your marriage good? Are your kids okay? You may have a $25 million plane, but is your marriage okay?

03:06:49.840 --> 03:06:55.676
Do your kids respect you? Are your kids blessing you? Do they talk about you?

03:06:55.677 --> 03:07:04.719
You may have millions in the bank, but are you healthy with your children?

03:07:04.720 --> 03:07:12.320
Probably not. But is that prosperity? I ask you that. Is that prosperity?

03:07:12.321 --> 03:07:18.904
If your marriage sucks and your kids are all strung out and they don't serve the Lord, is that prosperity?

03:07:18.905 --> 03:07:24.159
If you're a minister and that's happening, I don't see that as prosperous.

03:07:24.160 --> 03:07:34.524
I don't care how much you have in the bank. So, I guess your question to me is just—I don't know.

03:07:34.525 --> 03:07:40.064
Does that answer you, son? I think these people have prosperity backwards.

03:07:40.065 --> 03:07:45.879
Hollywood is not prosperous. They're committing suicide by the dozens a year.

03:07:45.880 --> 03:07:53.113
You know, you got these celebrities that have millions of dollars and they're driving a brand new Ferrari, but they're depressed and they're on Prozac.

03:07:53.114 --> 03:08:21.919
That's not prosperous. 'Can you come to California in January?'Brandon, I would think about it. I really like Brandon. Brandon Brimm is a good guy.

03:08:21.920 --> 03:08:30.617
He has a church that he's trying to do in Montecito, and you should go to his thing and help him if you live out there.

03:08:30.618 --> 03:08:33.233
California, there's a lot of people that don't have a good church out there.

03:08:33.234 --> 03:08:41.999
And you need people, Holy Ghost and fire. 'I'm going to see Billy Burke in Pennsylvania next month because of you.

03:08:42.000 --> 03:08:47.328
I can't wait.'Oh, it's going to be off the chain. You're going to love Billy Burke.

03:08:47.329 --> 03:08:58.452
In fact, that would be a fun meeting to go to. 'Would you be able to pray for me?

03:08:58.453 --> 03:09:03.310
I've been in some pain, bladder issue.'Father, I thank you, Lord, for healing her bladder.

03:09:03.311 --> 03:09:09.759
We call for the healing over her bladder in Jesus'name. We call for deliverance.

03:09:09.760 --> 03:09:17.913
No, I do not listen to Jonathan Shuttlesworth. 'The more I pray, the more I pull away from this spouse.

03:09:17.914 --> 03:09:26.477
11 years, kids. Please preach the truth.'Brandon, somebody please block.

03:09:26.478 --> 03:09:32.941
Somebody needs to block somebody. Some are trouble brewing.

03:09:32.942 --> 03:09:37.074
There's so many people. Is there a lot of trolls tonight? I don't ever see them.

03:09:37.075 --> 03:09:40.886
'Do you see demons?'Yeah, I see a lot of demons, but I don't talk about it.

03:09:40.887 --> 03:09:44.677
I left you hanging. Yeah, I needed to go to the bathroom myself after three years.

03:09:44.678 --> 03:09:49.650
You left me. I can't leave these people. Well, I couldn't come back over there.

03:09:49.651 --> 03:09:56.116
'Oh, do you see demons?'That's an interesting question. Do you know I never talk about the demons I see?

03:09:56.117 --> 03:10:01.913
I see—and I hate to say this, but there's a lot of times I see more of the demonic than I see anything else.

03:10:01.914 --> 03:10:09.994
But I never give it glory. Never. They don't deserve it. But God only shows it to me to help people.

03:10:09.995 --> 03:10:17.003
Sorry. Hey, good looking. I was trying not to make a... but I want to tell you this.

03:10:17.004 --> 03:10:20.836
The demonic loves when you see them. They want you to glorify.

03:10:20.837 --> 03:10:30.176
They like to be noticed. Pride wants to be noticed. And they are full of pride. That's all they are.

03:10:30.177 --> 03:10:38.433
And every single time I see them, I don't give them the satisfaction to show them that I see them because they are trash.

03:10:38.434 --> 03:10:47.205
And I say, "I ain't going to give you any glory."And I'm going to tell you, they're more apt to want to show up than angels.

03:10:47.206 --> 03:11:04.559
Angels are never about themselves. We focus the glory on Him because He deserves all the glory and all the recognition.

03:11:04.560 --> 03:11:13.919
Every single bit of it. Just like the Word says, even the rocks cry out. And we ain't going to let the rocks do our job.

03:11:13.920 --> 03:11:25.730
We're going to be a vessel used by Him to give Him all the honor, all the glory, and direct attract deflect it all to Him.

03:11:25.731 --> 03:11:31.519
To Him because He deserves everything we have. Everything.

03:11:31.520 --> 03:11:42.688
None of us. All of you. All of you, Lord. So, I went to get me some unsweet tea.

03:11:42.689 --> 03:11:48.628
Mine didn't have ice. So, I don't know why we're staying on so late.

03:11:48.629 --> 03:11:53.168
Maybe we should go, but I thought it was fun to answer some questions.

03:11:53.169 --> 03:11:59.176
Y'all are like me. You're just addicted to the glory and His presence.

03:11:59.177 --> 03:12:03.289
We're just having fun. I'm just talking and praying in the midnight hour.

03:12:03.290 --> 03:12:08.273
We are because of Him. She will be okay. I've had three brain surgeries.

03:12:08.274 --> 03:12:13.793
Yep. Thank you for talking to us. Lots of church people don't just answer questions and hang out.

03:12:13.794 --> 03:12:24.543
Yeah. That's why I don't like it either. I get tired of all the political church celebrity crap.

03:12:24.544 --> 03:12:30.318
Yeah. We're just real people. That's why, you know, I don't like it when I go to these meetings.

03:12:30.319 --> 03:12:38.274
When you think I'm anything more than just Brandon, I say, "Listen, go vertical."It's the same thing.

03:12:38.275 --> 03:12:45.908
Yes, we need Him. But when it comes down to a lot of these big pastors, I've seen a lot more now than I've ever seen.

03:12:45.909 --> 03:12:49.872
And I'm going to tell you this, folks: everybody has something they're going through.

03:12:49.873 --> 03:12:55.039
There's nobody that has it all together. We're all a work in progress.

03:12:55.040 --> 03:13:04.403
And we put our clothes on one leg at a time. We all wake up. We have to go to the bathroom. We all have stinky armpits. It's all just real.

03:13:04.404 --> 03:13:13.322
And if you start exalting somebody and thinking that they've got it together more than you—maybe they've worked their faith more.

03:13:13.323 --> 03:13:21.370
Maybe they've developed their faith more because it's just like anything: if you do something long enough, you're going to get good at it.

03:13:21.371 --> 03:13:25.305
But the Lord said this to me, which was interesting. We talked about it.

03:13:25.306 --> 03:13:33.759
You have a lot of people that are fakers that have learned to be good parrots.

03:13:33.760 --> 03:13:38.368
They don't have a revelation of it. A parrot—the Lord said they are parrots.

03:13:38.369 --> 03:13:46.168
There's a lot of parrots in the body of Christ. He said, "Brandon, a lot of parroting comes from—a parrot just mocks.

03:13:46.169 --> 03:13:57.358
A parrot doesn't say it on its own. A parrot just has the ability to repeat what it knows."But it doesn't mean it has a revelation of it.

03:13:57.359 --> 03:14:10.799
It is just squawking, whatever. But it's not something that understands even what it's saying.

03:14:10.800 --> 03:14:14.291
And that's why He said a lot of the body of Christ is doing that.

03:14:14.292 --> 03:14:19.077
They're just parroting because it's Christianese, especially in the charismatic circle.

03:14:19.078 --> 03:14:24.616
But it's not sinking in. It's not revelation to them. They don't have it inside of their heart.

03:14:24.617 --> 03:14:31.039
What did He say about you? And I've known this. I see this on leadership.

03:14:31.040 --> 03:14:37.176
And they'll say it and the Lord said, "That's not real to her. That's not real to him.

03:14:37.177 --> 03:14:51.599
They're parroting them."That's why the Word said you will know them by their fruit—not by what they say, but by what their fruit is.

03:14:51.600 --> 03:14:57.350
I heard tonight; I heard marching in the sky. I don't know what that means.

03:14:57.351 --> 03:15:09.528
I don't know either. I love it. But you can see it though. And that's why He talked to me about nepotism. And He's been talking to me more about nepotism.

03:15:09.529 --> 03:15:31.528
He said, "You'll see a lot of the elders go home and they'll try to pass it on to their kids and they're not qualified for the mantle of the anointing on that ministry, and the ministry will self-implode because you feel that you are qualified because you have blood from that individual.

03:15:31.529 --> 03:15:52.719
Well, I'm part of the family."And the Lord warned me and He said, "Pray for a lot of these mega ministries that are older because they don't have a successor that has been through the refining fire."And if you've not been through the refining fire, you'll not sustain the ministry the way it should because of nepotism.

03:15:52.720 --> 03:15:58.276
He said, "Just because you're in the bloodline doesn't mean you're qualified for it."That's what He said to me.

03:15:58.277 --> 03:16:11.659
He said, "Pray, for a great shaking is coming to certain ministries."It's like David with the armor that's too big that doesn't fit.

03:16:11.660 --> 03:16:22.719
Does that make sense? Because it happens a lot. And I see this happening in more ministries, but the Lord warns me specifically it's going to happen a lot in 2026.

03:16:22.720 --> 03:16:29.754
And He said, "You will see this in 2026. Pray for these ministries, son, for there is nepotism.

03:16:29.755 --> 03:16:39.278
And they think they're qualified and they're not. Only qualification is through the refining fire."And He warned me about this.

03:16:39.279 --> 03:16:46.969
And I said, "Okay."And He said a lot of the nepotism is they're just parroting what they heard their mama say or they heard their daddy say.

03:16:46.970 --> 03:16:54.477
It wasn't really rooted in their heart because they were able to coast on the coattails of that family member.

03:16:54.478 --> 03:17:12.777
And He said, "You'll see true fruit of who they really are in the days ahead because the ministry will die."And I said, "Whoa, that's a hard word, but that's what You warned me about."Does that make sense?

03:17:12.778 --> 03:17:23.599
And it shook me because I told my boy, I said, "Listen, no matter what happens to me, you better get a revelation of who Jesus is to you.

03:17:23.600 --> 03:17:27.580
Don't ever ride on daddy's coattails thinking you could ride on my faith.

03:17:27.581 --> 03:17:34.958
You must find Him by yourself, son. You must have a revelation."I told Dina the same thing. I said, "You never can ride.

03:17:34.959 --> 03:17:45.091
If God forbid anything happened to me, you must know Him intimately by yourself, not just what Brandon knows or whatever."And we talk about it that way. You must find Him.

03:17:45.092 --> 03:17:55.995
And she said, "That's right."Having an intimate relationship with the Father by yourself, regardless of your spouse, regardless of who you are, you must have it.

03:17:55.996 --> 03:18:03.918
And Diana has it. She seeks Him more than I do. She has more prayer time than I do.

03:18:03.919 --> 03:18:19.890
I go, "Look at you, girl."But you know, listening to the Word, stirring yourself up and keeping that fire going. Wow.

03:18:19.891 --> 03:18:28.633
"Why does it keep going like that, honey?""It goes because you stop it because you're scrolling up and then it stops automatically scrolling for you."Oh, is that how it does that?

03:18:28.635 --> 03:18:33.782
Yeah. So, you can tell I don't know what I'm doing. You have your thumb on it so it stays there.

03:18:33.783 --> 03:18:46.507
Seek God. When will you visit San Antonio, Texas? I don't know. I've been to San Antonio one time. I've been to the Alamo.

03:18:46.508 --> 03:18:50.821
And the Lord taught me about the witchcraft that goes on around the Alamo and the things that were there.

03:18:50.822 --> 03:18:55.950
And I saw that about the blood sacrifices that happened with the Alamo.

03:18:55.951 --> 03:19:03.954
It was funny because every single time, He always teaches me things when I go into these cities, and I'm able to go in about the Alamo and the things that happened there.

03:19:03.955 --> 03:19:13.280
And there's darkness around that. But it's interesting. When will you have a physical meeting?

03:19:13.281 --> 03:19:17.309
I don't know. I never thought about having a physical meeting.

