03:21:53.820 --> 03:21:58.064
Ministry came out of being free, being able to work for yourself.

03:21:58.065 --> 03:22:06.311
I didn't have to wake up and go to my job—like tomorrow at one o'clock in the morning—and go, 'Hey, we need to go to bed because we got to get up.'Because we work for ourselves.

03:22:06.312 --> 03:22:15.438
And like I said, being rich is irrelevant to what you consider rich. How much money do you need to make it?

03:22:15.439 --> 03:22:28.449
