03:24:17.096 --> 03:24:27.650
God says, 'Yes, have a meeting, Brandon.'Believe in him. Healing already gave you head of the new music.

03:24:27.651 --> 03:24:39.519
Only the Lord knows. Come to Cleveland, Tennessee. I thought about it because Perry is there.

03:24:39.520 --> 03:24:44.064
I don't know if some of these people like me; I'm just being real with you.

03:24:44.065 --> 03:24:47.006
If I went to Cleveland and I went to Perry's church, maybe he doesn't like me.

03:24:47.007 --> 03:24:51.276
That's a lot of my insecurities, thinking if I showed up at Perry's church, he's like, 'I don't like that guy.

03:24:51.277 --> 03:24:55.366
Get him out of here.'You don't know. I just don't try to impose on anybody.

03:24:55.367 --> 03:25:04.704
I just show up and say, 'Hey, if I see Billy Burke there, I'll go and visit.'But I don't know if some of these ministers even think I'm authentic or whatever.

03:25:04.705 --> 03:25:16.022
If the Lord said for us to go, we would go. No, I don't see 24 angels. No, I see them. I see them when the Lord allows me to.

03:25:16.023 --> 03:25:24.677
Like I saw that angel that I told you all about for several hours afterward and he talked to us.

03:25:24.678 --> 03:25:32.337
And then it just lifted; the mantle of how I see comes on like a cloak. I feel it.

03:25:32.338 --> 03:25:37.872
I always tell her I can feel it when it comes on and I feel it when it lifts off.

03:25:37.873 --> 03:25:44.113
When that glory comes on me, I feel it and then I start seeing.

03:25:44.114 --> 03:25:48.879
It lasts sometimes hours, sometimes just a couple minutes.

03:25:48.880 --> 03:25:55.008
But when it comes on me heavy, I see a lot. I can see it on people.

03:25:55.009 --> 03:25:59.628
I can see stuff. But it only happens whenever the Lord wills.

03:25:59.629 --> 03:26:06.126
I don't control it. It's only when he says it's okay and he allows it.

03:26:06.127 --> 03:26:09.928
If he wants me, I don't see all the time. It's only whenever the anointing comes on.

03:26:09.929 --> 03:26:15.517
